    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "concurrency_note",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 962,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 46,
      "text": "No asyncio.Queue: tick() directly awaits dispatch_fn for each due task in serial order.\nThe Spawner's asyncio.Semaphore (not a queue) provides backpressure \u2014 scheduler blocks awaiting a free LLM session slot.\nDeterministic jobs (registry path) skip the Spawner entirely: they run inline as Python coroutines.",
      "originalText": "No asyncio.Queue: tick() directly awaits dispatch_fn for each due task in serial order.\nThe Spawner's asyncio.Semaphore (not a queue) provides backpressure \u2014 scheduler blocks awaiting a free LLM session slot.\nDeterministic jobs (registry path) skip the Spawner entirely: they run inline as Python coroutines.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
