    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "isolation_note",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1202,
      "width": 960,
      "height": 32,
      "text": "Each butler runs in its own OS process (separate daemon). No shared scheduler state. Inter-butler communication is MCP-only through Switchboard.\nstagger_key = butler name \u2192 SHA-256 deterministic offset prevents thundering herd even when multiple butlers share the same cron boundary.",
      "originalText": "Each butler runs in its own OS process (separate daemon). No shared scheduler state. Inter-butler communication is MCP-only through Switchboard.\nstagger_key = butler name \u2192 SHA-256 deterministic offset prevents thundering herd even when multiple butlers share the same cron boundary.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
