    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "buf_contrast_note",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 2060,
      "width": 860,
      "height": 48,
      "text": "Key distinction: Scheduler fires tasks on a cron schedule (time-driven), writing trigger_source=\"schedule:<name>\" to the Spawner.\nMessage Buffer handles inbound messages (event-driven), routing via priority tiers to pipeline.process() \u2192 Spawner.\nBoth paths share the same Spawner and its asyncio.Semaphore backpressure \u2014 concurrent slot budget is shared.",
      "originalText": "Key distinction: Scheduler fires tasks on a cron schedule (time-driven), writing trigger_source=\"schedule:<name>\" to the Spawner.\nMessage Buffer handles inbound messages (event-driven), routing via priority tiers to pipeline.process() \u2192 Spawner.\nBoth paths share the same Spawner and its asyncio.Semaphore backpressure \u2014 concurrent slot budget is shared.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
